00:03:57.750 --> 00:04:00.790 align:middle line:84%
I didn't ask you
to trust me, did I?

00:04:00.790 --> 00:04:02.190 align:middle line:90%
Did I ask you to trust me?

00:04:02.190 --> 00:04:02.990 align:middle line:90%
What did I say?

00:04:02.990 --> 00:04:04.450 align:middle line:90%
Tell me.

00:04:04.450 --> 00:04:06.880 align:middle line:84%
I said, you can take your
sleeping bag if you like,

00:04:06.880 --> 00:04:08.533 align:middle line:90%
but you would not need it.

00:04:08.533 --> 00:04:10.450 align:middle line:84%
I think you don't need
your sleeping bags, no.

00:04:10.450 --> 00:04:11.830 align:middle line:90%
