because he wants to buy food?

00:07:46.490 --> 00:07:51.730 align:middle line:90%


00:07:51.730 --> 00:07:52.760 align:middle line:90%
How are we different?

00:07:52.760 --> 00:07:54.910 align:middle line:84%
It's just that we are in
a different circumstantial

00:07:54.910 --> 00:07:56.170 align:middle line:90%
reality.

00:07:56.170 --> 00:07:58.660 align:middle line:84%
If we were put in that
circumstantial reality, who

00:07:58.660 --> 00:08:00.900 align:middle line:90%
knows what will come out of us.

00:08:00.900 --> 00:08:01.700 align:middle line:90%
Is it not?

00:08:01.700 --> 00:08:06.300 align:middle line:90%


00:08:06.300 --> 00:08:07.290 align:middle line:90%
It takes courage.

00:08:07.290 --> 00:08:10.500 align:middle line:90%
It demands absolute totality--

00:08:10.500 --> 00:08:11.300 align:middle line:90%
nothing short.

00:08:11.300 --> 00:08:16.200 align:middle line:90%


00:08:16.200 --> 00:08:17.680 align:middle line:90%
Hmm?

